			<h3 ><a href="#p169784">Re: How to read 小火</a></h3>
			<p class="author"><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/viewtopic.php?p=169784&amp;sid=d2e36d4acb2f8e4119698751e0026a72#p169784"><img src="http://thejapanesepage.com/phpbb/styles/tjp-embed/imageset/icon_post_target.gif" width="11" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" /></a>by <strong><a href="http://thejapanesepage.com/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=107271&amp;sid=d2e36d4acb2f8e4119698751e0026a72">Cath</a></strong> &raquo; Thu 04.14.2011 4:20 pm </p>

			

